It’s been just over a month since we announced our $100,000 donation to support those impacted by the #MarshallFires. We are excited to share that Yasso has made an incremental donation of $100,000, and thanks to a lengthy list of incredibly generous brands, businesses, and individual donors, we have hit the $1MM mark!

All of the proceeds are going to families who have lost their homes, and need support to get back on their feet. Yasso's mission is to deliver joy to those in our community when they need it most, and we couldn't think of a better moment to do so.

If you are interested in helping, we've linked the GoFundMe in our bio. We sincerely thank everyone who has contributed so far!
